com.yantra.yfc.rcp

Class YRCCacheManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yantra.yfc.rcp.YRCCacheManager

  • public class YRCCacheManager
extends java.lang.Object
    The class providing base implementation for caching data A plugin can use this class to cache data used it again
    The class provides methods to add/modify/clear cache. The cache is maintained separately for each Plugin and each plugin cache has a MAX SIZE of Cache. To maintane MAX SIZE, Least Recently Used (LRU algorithm is used.
    Since:
    3.0
    Author:
    vvinocha
